 *******************************************************************************
 ************************
 This is a test program to verify  whether the force are the derivative of the e
 nergy: F=-dE/dR
It performs the integration of the calculated forces over   5 random displacement (in the range [-0.0100,0.0100] a.u.)
 and compares the result with the difference of the energy  between the final an
 d the initial position: E2-E1 = -Integral F.dR
  The advantage is two fold: 1) avoiding cancellation error in finite difference
  derivative, 2) considernig the forces over all atoms 
